# Trivy vulnerability ignore file
# Format: one CVE-ID or GHSA-ID per line, optionally followed by an expiry date
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-12345
#   GHSA-xxxx-yyyy-zzzz until:2026-06-01
#
# Add entries here for accepted risks or vulnerabilities with no available fix
# when ignore-unfixed: true in the workflow does not cover them.
